<paragraph id="9618B11398EA8A44AF209435BCA169DE" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
Holotype ♂, &quot;Iran, [prov.] Khorassan NP [National Park] Golestan, Almeh 1770 m 2.5.2001 
<geoCoordinate id="E57C55136921EDB2A88227DDCAEE2AFF" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="9" value="37.345833">37°20,75'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="71032A99A4A650F84CFE7C272D06DCEA" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="9" value="56.117">56°07,02'E</geoCoordinate>
leg. P. Huemer&quot; &quot;BC TLMF Lep 03782&quot; &quot;P. Huemer GEL 1241 ♂&quot; (TLMF). Paratypes. Iran. 4 ♂, same data as holotype, but BC TLMF Lep 03780, 03781 (TLMF).
</paragraph>
